metadata.name: OMFC AccessPass #1
metadata.description: Access passes will be used to gain access to the Official Maradona Fan Club, and will have utility and unlock multiple perks on the web and in the real world. A smart contract will randomly select 500 Access Pass holders from the pool of 5,000 passes, to be airdropped a Stage Two NFT from which TWO Access Pass Holders will win flights, accommodation, and match tickets
